---
---
<section id="komitmen" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--color-background-light)] -z-20"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="reveal opacity-0 scale-95 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
      <p class="text-base md:text-xl uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--color-emerald-glow)] mb-4 font-semibold">Komitmen</p>
      <h2 class="reveal-header text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text)] uppercase tracking-tight mb-12">
        Komitmen <span class="text-gradient">Kerjasama</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card-entry glass-panel p-8 md:p-14 mb-16">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-base md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>Kami percaya bahwa setiap individu memiliki potensi unik yang dapat berkembang secara optimal apabila dikenali dan diarahkan dengan tepat.</p>
        <p>PT Potensia Mitra Insani siap menjadi mitra strategis bagi institusi dalam menghadirkan program pengembangan yang terukur, aplikatif dan berkelanjutan.</p>
        <p>Kami membuka peluang kerjasama dengan berbagai pihak demi terciptanya peningkatan kualitas Sumber Daya Manusia yang lebih baik.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Growth Image with Glass Frame -->
    <div class="reveal opacity-0 translate-y-10 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out">
      <div class="w-full h-[350px] md:h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_30px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] animate-[var(--animate-anti-gravity-slow)] relative group border border-[var(--color-glass-border)]">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[var(--color-background)] via-transparent to-transparent z-10"></div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466692476868-aef1dfb1e735?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" alt="Pertumbuhan Tunas" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000" loading="lazy" />
        <!-- Emerald tint overlay -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[rgba(74,222,128,0.05)] mix-blend-overlay"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="section-glow-line mt-24"></div>
</section>
